      "review_id": "Sye1Z22R5B",
      "rebuttal_id": "Hkl2wG0joB",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "text": "The prior work by Hsu et al. showed that the oracle trained by deep learning has high accuracy (see Section 5.3 in their paper): for Internet traffic data, the AUC score is 0.9, and for search query data, the AUC score is 0.8.",
